Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.name: start
Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.abstract: Start angle of the ring line. Ranges from 0.0 to 1.0.

Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.name: end
Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.abstract: End angle of the ring line. Ranges from 0.0 to 1.0.

Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.name: clockwise
Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.abstract: Whether the ring should animate in a clockwise direction.

Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.name: lineWidth
Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.abstract: Width of the ring line relative to its container. Ranges from 0.0 to 1.0.

Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.name: overlaps
Structs/ActivityRing.html#/s:19GCActivit.abstract: Whether the ring line should overlap its preceding ActivityRing

Structs/ActivityRing.html.name: ActivityRing
Structs/ActivityRing.html.abstract: Models an individual ring in a GCActivityIndicator.

Classes/GCActivityIndicator.html#/s:19GC.name: hidesWhenStopped
Classes/GCActivityIndicator.html#/s:19GC.abstract: Whether the view should hide when animation stops.

Classes/GCActivityIndicator.html.name: GCActivityIndicator
Classes/GCActivityIndicator.html.abstract: Models a view with some number of activity indicator rings.
